Detailed Description

An implementation of DSF metadata.

This is an implementation of DSF metadata using an ID3v2 tag inside the metadata chunk. The DSF specification is located at http://dsd-guide.com/sites/default/files/white-papers/DSFFileFormatSpec_E.pdf
